name: 3-stage-motor-driven-compressor-control-system-for-natural-gas-using-labview
body: The aim of the project is to simulate the basic functioning of a 3-Stage Reciprocating Compressor for Natural Gas and the various safety inter-locks involved. ### Please Note: The "FINAL_PROJECT.vi" is the main VI file, the rest are subVIs. This VI won't execute with LabVIEW version below 2014. ### Human Machine Interface: (Click on the image for the larger view) ![output](https://cloud.githubusercontent.com/assets/17741974/16179894/4be2bc78-3674-11e6-86c1-c7e5b12c3501.jpg) ### Historical Trend: (Click on the image for the larger view) ![output3](https://cloud.githubusercontent.com/assets/17741974/16179900/79038eee-3674-11e6-81e1-40b77d7d7cf8.jpg) ![output2](https://cloud.githubusercontent.com/assets/17741974/16179899/6bc785a0-3674-11e6-9db2-1c17aa35e378.jpg) ### Safety Interlock (Fire Suppression System): (Click on the image for the larger view) ![output4](https://cloud.githubusercontent.com/assets/17741974/16179920/2cda0150-3675-11e6-9f72-736fe18515b9.jpg) ### Support or Contact (https://github.com/sagarkunder) and Iâ€™ll help you sort it out.
